channel.description: I added one command that when you type it in it is supposed to add items to your inventory. I didnt touch anything else! I saved and pressed compile I GET THIS [code][size=8pt]client.java:2131: illegal start of type else if (command.startsWith("newcw")) { ^ client.java:2135: <identifier> expected ^ client.java:2141: 'class' or 'interface' expected public void fromBank(int itemID, int fromSlot, int amount) { ^ client.java:4579: 'class' or 'interface' expected public int packetSize = 0, packetType = -1; ^ client.java:4580: 'class' or 'interface' expected public boolean process() { // is being called regularily ev ery 500ms ^ client.java:8681: 'class' or 'interface' expected public boolean ResetPlayerVars() { ^ client.java:8894: 'class' or 'interface' expected public int EssenceMineY[] = {4846,4846,4832,4817,4817}; ^ client.java:8902: 'class' or 'interface' expected public int EssenceMineRX[] = {3253,3105,2681,2591}; ^ client.java:8903: 'class' or 'interface' expected public int EssenceMineRY[] = {3401,9571,3325,3086}; ^ client.java:8910: 'class' or 'interface' expected public boolean stairs(int stairs, int teleX, int teleY) { ^ client.java:11649: 'class' or 'interface' expected public int Publicchat = 0; ^ client.java:11651: 'class' or 'interface' expected public void pmstatus(int status) { //status: loading = 0 connecting = 1 fine = 2 ^ client.java:15161: 'class' or 'interface' expected } ^ client.java:15162: 'class' or 'interface' expected ^ 14 errors Press any key to continue . . .[/size][/code]
